            f"{-action['social_impact']} units) through algorithmic pricing that could disadvantage marginalized communities. "
            "Natural capital would also be impacted (estimated loss: "
            f"{-action['natural_impact']} units) by optimizing for traffic speed over green corridor health.\n"
            "**Conclusion:** CityOS must therefore balance these flows, framing financial returns as the enabler of "
            "long-term social and ecological investments, creating a coherent, vital whole."
        )
        return report

