                "Establish a 'Digital Community Asset Trust' on the CityOS platform to register and manage communal assets (e.g., public spaces, informal markets), protecting them from foreign speculative investment.",
                "Repurpose abandoned industrial sites as 'Smart Commons' - tech-enabled hubs for local production and skills-sharing, with access and resource management governed by the CityOS citizen identity system."
